item.title: Nord Stream Pipelines leaks seen from space
item.author: Francesco Mancuso
item.description: Nord Stream Pipelines leaks seen from space Three leaks have been reported near the island of Bornholm, two pipelines running underwater from Russia to Germany were damaged some days ago. Main Image Image Credits - Fig.1 - 4K Mountains Wallpaper First leak Image Credits - Fig.2 - 4K Mountains Wallpaper Other leaks Image Credits - Fig.3 - 4K Mountains Wallpaper What does the tweets say #GasLeak This seems to be one of the gas leaks of the #nordstream1 or #nordstream2 gas pipelines in the #Baltic Sea.
